@startuml Sequence_Candidate_JobSearch
title Ứng Viên - Tìm Kiếm Công Việc (Module B, E)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant JobService as "Job\nService"
participant MatchingService as "Matching\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Tìm Kiếm Công Việc ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Tìm việc làm"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show search/filter form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Nhập: từ khóa, filter location/salary
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs?keyword=java&location=...&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: Return jobs list
JobService --> FrontEnd: Jobs (20 results)
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị danh sách công việc

== Xem Chi Tiết Công Việc ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click vào 1 công việc
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}
JobService -> Database: Get tin_tuyen_dung + details
Database --> JobService: Job details
JobService --> FrontEnd: Full job info
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị chi tiết job

== Xem Match Score ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: (on job detail page)
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: GET /api/matching/score\n(cvId={candidateDefaultCV}, jobId={jobId})
MatchingService -> Database: Get CV skills & job requirements
Database --> MatchingService: Skills & requirements
MatchingService -> MatchingService: Calculate match score
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: Match score (80%)
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị "Độ phù hợp: 80%"

== Lọc Công Việc ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Bộ lọc nâng cao"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show filter modal
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Chọn: ngành, địa điểm, mức lương, loại hình
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs\n?industries=...&locations=...\n&salaryMin=...&salaryMax=...\n&employmentTypes=...&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query with filters
Database --> JobService: Filtered results
JobService --> FrontEnd: Jobs list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị kết quả lọc

== Tìm Kiếm Theo Địa Điểm ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Filter by location
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs?locations=TP.HCM,Hà Nội&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query tin_tuyen_dung (locations)
Database --> JobService: Jobs
JobService --> FrontEnd: Filtered jobs
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị công việc theo địa điểm

== Tìm Kiếm Theo Mức Lương ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Set salary range
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs?salaryMin=10000000&salaryMax=30000000&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query by salary range
Database --> JobService: Jobs matching salary
JobService --> FrontEnd: Jobs list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị công việc theo mức lương

== Tìm Kiếm Theo Ngành ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Select industries
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs?industries=IT,BANKING&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query tin_tuyen_dung (industries)
Database --> JobService: Jobs in selected industries
JobService --> FrontEnd: Jobs list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị công việc theo ngành

== Lưu Tìm Kiếm (Future) ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Lưu tìm kiếm này"
note right of Candidate
  Future feature:
  Save search criteria for recommendations
end note

@enduml
